channel.description: *Turkish Cuisine* is a project to introduce Turkish kitchen to people all around the world. All content is licensed under [Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License](http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/).

item.title: Mücver
item.description: Mücver is a Turkish fritter, similar to a pancake made from grated squash, courgette or potatoes, egg, onion, dill, cheese and flour.
